trans-unit.source: Represents a static header item on a smart tag panel.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en statisk rubrikobjektet på en panel med smarta etiketter.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: Like the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionTextItem> base class, DesignerActionHeaderItem represents individual static text items in a smart tag panel.
trans-unit.target: Exempel på <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionTextItem>basklass DesignerActionHeaderItem representerar enskilda statisk textobjekt i en panel med smarta etiketter.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionTextItem>

trans-unit.source: However, DesignerActionHeaderItem entries are displayed using bold text.
trans-unit.target: Dock visas DesignerActionHeaderItem posterna med fetstil.

trans-unit.source: Typically, a header item is used to create a heading for a group of items in a panel.
trans-unit.target: Normalt används en rubrikobjektet för att skapa en rubrik för en grupp med objekt på en panel.

trans-unit.source: Clicking on a header item causes no action.
trans-unit.target: Klicka på en rubrikobjektet gör ingenting.

trans-unit.source: Individual panel items are associated together to form a panel by calling the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList.GetSortedActionItems%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> class.
trans-unit.target: Enskilda objekt som är associerade tillsammans för att bilda en panel genom att anropa <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList.GetSortedActionItems%2A>metoden i <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>klassen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList.GetSortedActionItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"></xref> class using the provided name string.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av den angivna strängen.

trans-unit.source: This constructor sets both the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.DisplayName%2A> and the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Category%2A> properties to the value of the `displayName` parameter and sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A> property to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Den här konstruktorn anger både den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.DisplayName%2A>och <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Category%2A>egenskaper till värdet för den `displayName` parametern och anger den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A>egenskapen `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Category%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The text to be displayed in the header.
trans-unit.target: Texten som ska visas i rubriken.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"></xref> class using the provided name and category strings.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"> </xref> klassen med angivet namn och kategori strängar.

trans-unit.source: This constructor sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A> property to `null`.
The text to be displayed in the header.
trans-unit.target: Texten som ska visas i rubriken.

trans-unit.source: The case-sensitive <xref:System.String> that defines the groupings of panel entries.
trans-unit.target: De skiftlägeskänsliga <xref:System.String>som definierar grupperingar av panelen poster.</xref:System.String>
